g/\" target=\"_blank\">annual letters</a>, where they take stock of the Gates Foundation and the world. And follow his ongoing thinking on his personal website, <a href=\"http://www.thegatesnotes.com/\" target=\"_blank\">The Gates Notes</a>. His new paper, &quot;The Next Epidemic,&quot; is published by the <em>New England Journal of Medicine.</em>    </p>"}],"speaker_name":"Bill and Melinda Gates","tags":["activism","business","money","philanthropy"],"title":"Why giving away our wealth has been the most satisfying thing we've done","video_type":{"id":"1","name":"TED Stage Talk"},"viewed_count":3487272}]}
